{"tid":2264194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府將推「安心出行」App 場所現感染風險即發通知","createTime":"2020-10-30T12:36:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T12:46:47.000Z","uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"41f1c4de00b6c2a8ef2a35c9ff84059984aa708f","tid":2264194,"uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1557566_1_L_20201030201422.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1557566_1_L_20201030201422.jpg&h=157429ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府招標製作感染風險通知流動應用程式，讓市民記錄行蹤，將命名為「安心出行」。程式為市民提供便利的數碼工具，自行記錄他們的出行記錄，方便商戶記錄到訪其場所的客戶。如場所出現感染個案，流動應用程式會向用戶發出通知。若用戶不幸確診，衞生防護中心會連絡用戶提供出行記錄，以協助追尋相關接觸者。<br />\n<br />\n康樂及文化事務署已提供164個室內設施張貼二維碼，包括115個體育館、45個游泳池及4個其他場地(單車館、展覽館、活動室等)。食環署也已提供97個場地張貼二維碼，包括23個熟食市場和74個街市。<br />\n<br />\n場所營運者可自願登記，市民也可自行下載使用「安心出行」應用程式。市民可應用程式登記姓名及聯絡資料保存於應用程式內，資料不會上傳到任何中央資料庫 。"},{"pid":"1d82eac56c58bb839d73432ca735317b6002fb9b","tid":2264194,"uid":224533,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:40:55.000Z","msg":"呢個先係香港人嘅安心出行<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TYBMauN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTYBMauN.jpg&h=9c84894b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a89677a8306f93275b16f618a320e709f377f230","tid":2264194,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LwE6avr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLwE6avr.png&h=bf1ea285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府唔用呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd6a105278a53b576d0bd4ecde5c1cdf346aae1","tid":2264194,"uid":83582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:43:30.000Z","msg":"「安心上路」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7e2ba29b573b6f9cea2e177716f5cc79952350","tid":2264194,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:46:47.000Z","msg":"安心上路APP<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}